creator: Onze Stad App
descriptionHtml:
De Affligem City-App is een messenger waarmee je met de locale overheid, handelaars, zorgverstrekkers, verenigingen en vrienden kan communiceren. Koppel u met uw lokale handelaars, verenigingen, zorgverstrekkers en u zal kunnen genieten van digitale communicatie om zaken te bestellen, reserveren, ..., nieuws te ontvangen.
Kortom, de Affligem City-App is uw mobiele toegangspoort tot alle diensten in uw gemeente.

creator: Onze Stad App
descriptionHtml:
The Affligem City-App is a messenger for communicating with the local government, merchants, care institutions and associations.
Connect with your local merchants, associations and care institutions and you will be able to enjoy digital communication to order products, make reservations, receive news, ...
In short, the Affligem City-App is your mobile gateway to all services in your region.
